  "description": "<b>宏董事长王振堂周一在接受路透社采访时表示，到明年或后年，宏80%的产品都将采用触摸屏技术。宏希望平板电脑和触摸屏笔记本能推动PC销售。</b>王振堂表示，到今年底，触摸屏设备销量将占宏笔记本总销量的30%至35%，高于这一季度的25%。宏目前是全球排名第4的PC厂商。今年第一季度，宏的平板电脑出货量为120万台，而今年全年的出货量目标为500万至1000万台。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cc61bc5/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239731.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%8F%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%96%E5%90%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%8F80%25%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%A6%E6%91%B8%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239731.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%8F%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%96%E5%90%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%8F80%25%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%A6%E6%91%B8%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239731.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%8F%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%96%E5%90%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%8F80%25%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%A6%E6%91%B8%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239731.htm&amp;t=%E5%AE%8F%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%96%E5%90%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%AE%8F80%25%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%A6%E6%91%B8%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=htt